textAfterTable: 13 Songs Album Review The Classical Child's Christmas is a festive collection of favorite Christmas classics that kids and adults will love. It features delightful and unique arrangements of well-loved selections from Handel's "Messiah," and Bach's "Christmas Oratorio," Tchaikovsky's "Nutcracker Suite," and Corelli's "Christmas Concerto." Young listeners will also enjoy many charming traditional Christmas carols like "Hark the Herald Angels," "Joy to the World," and "The Ukrainian Bell Carol..."
